# Fluff Date: 2026-03-18 15:07:44
<overview>
<p>The Free Worlds League's fractious politics have always made centralized BattleMech procurement difficult, pushing the FWLM toward heavy investment in conventional infantry to fill the gaps. Towing crew-served autocannon/20 field guns, these platoons deploy the heaviest conventional direct-fire weapon available to infantry formations. A single AC/20 round can cripple a light vehicle or breach BattleMech armor at short range, though the weapon's bulk limits repositioning.</p>
</overview>

